text: Ilikovo () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Gorkovsky Selsoviet, Kushnarenkovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 541 as of 2010. There are 5 streets. == Geography == It is located 34 km from Kushnarenkovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kushnarenkovsky District
title: Ilikovo
